# Carto has a known peer-dependency conflict: tree-sitter@0.25.0 vs
# tree-sitter-c-sharp@0.21.3 (which declares peer tree-sitter@^0.21.0).
# Both work fine at runtime — the C# grammar is ABI-compatible with
# tree-sitter 0.25 — but npm 7+ refuses to resolve without this flag.
#
# Resolution path: upgrade tree-sitter-c-sharp once a version compatible
# with tree-sitter@0.25 is published. Until then, this flag is required
# for any npm install / npm ci in this repo.
legacy-peer-deps=true
